# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:84
translate korean e08s01_40e3b63d:

    # arj "What's this?"
    arj "이게 뭐야?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:87
translate korean e08s01_686a1a72:

    # mc "It's for you. My flower."
    mc "널 위해 내가 준비한 꽃."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:90
translate korean e08s01_022a1e3a:

    # arj "Aw. That's cute."
    arj "어우. 예뻐라."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:93
translate korean e08s01_5d145c03:

    # mc "Since there's no roses growing around here, this one I named after you."
    mc "무슨 꽃인지는 몰라도 예쁘더라구. 이 근처에는 장미가 안 피잖아. 그래서 이 꽃에 네 이름을 붙였지."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:99
translate korean e08s01_49a753e9:

    # mc "I have an app on my phone that identifies the names of different flowers and stuff."
    mc "참, 휴대폰에 꽃 같은 거 이름 확인하는 앱이 있는데."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:100
translate korean e08s01_a8a5e648:

    # mc "This one is called... don't kill me?"
    mc "이 꽃 이름은... 말해도 화내지 마?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:102
translate korean e08s01_ff25483d:

    # arj "That's a weird name for a flower."
    arj "꽃 치곤 이름이 특이한데."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:104
translate korean e08s01_022a4456:

    # mc "No. It's called Lydia."
    mc "아, 그게 아니라. 이 꽃 이름 말인데, 리디아야."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:107
translate korean e08s01_fcc7bb93:

    # arj "Lydia?"
    arj "리디아?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:109
translate korean e08s01_a87a337b:

    # mc "Yep."
    mc "응."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:110
translate korean e08s01_e15a70a6:

    # arj "Really?"
    arj "진짜로?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:113
translate korean e08s01_56471a62:

    # mc "Yeah. I'm not even making that up. In French, it's called a fleur-de-Lydia."
    mc "응. 지어낸 거 아냐. 프랑스어로, 플레-드-리디아라는 이름이래."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:115
translate korean e08s01_9e281d9a:

    # arj "Well, now I don't want it."
    arj "에휴, 듣기만 해도 싫어지네."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:116
translate korean e08s01_248c54d2:

    # mc "It's a good thing we don't live in France."
    mc "우리가 프랑스에 살지 않아서 다행이라니까."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:119
translate korean e08s01_7ac94059:

    # arj "I don't mind Lydia. Where do you think she's at now?"
    arj "난 이제 리디아는 신경 안 쓸 거야. 걔가 어디 있는진 너도 모르잖아?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:121
translate korean e08s01_537df6bc:

    # mc "Probably not on a farm, I can tell you that much."
    mc "적어도 농장에서는 안 보이는 거 같더라. 뭐 나라고 알겠어."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:122
translate korean e08s01_af924cef:

    # arj "Hope you don't mind that I'm all dirty."
    arj "나 더러운데 괜찮지?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:125
translate korean e08s01_abd46aeb:

    # mc "Of course I don't mind. Compared to the farm, you smell wonderful."
    mc "물론 괜찮지. 농장에 비하면, 향기가 난다고 해도 될 정도인걸."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:127
translate korean e08s01_61bf804b:

    # arj "Wow, such a compliment."
    arj "와아, 말솜씨 좀 봐."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:128
translate korean e08s01_efb8a0fb:

    # mc "Well, I mean, we switched to using fresh cow dung instead of composting with eggshells."
    mc "음, 있잖아. 우리 비료를 달걀 껍질에서 신선한 소똥으로 바꾸었잖아."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:131
translate korean e08s01_df1a7216:

    # arj "It's more organic."
    arj "이 편이 더 유기농이니까."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:133
translate korean e08s01_49c6ffe2:

    # mc "Oh, I know."
    mc "아, 그렇지."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:134
translate korean e08s01_88b407f3:

    # mc "Why is it that the most healthy stuff in nature always ends up smelling the worst?"
    mc "그런데 왜 자연이든 몸이든 좋다고 하는 것들에선 항상 악취에 가까운 냄새가 날까?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:137
translate korean e08s01_63fd3f91:

    # arj "What do you mean?"
    arj "무슨 소리야?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:139
translate korean e08s01_e3f3f4a4:

    # mc "You know, like kale."
    mc "너도 알잖아, 케일 같은 거."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:140
translate korean e08s01_43d9dcf2:

    # arj "Kale, huh? You just mean lettuce in general, right?"
    arj "케일, 응? 상추 같은 거 말하는 거니?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:143
translate korean e08s01_8a497fa4:

    # mc "I meant health foods. Anything green."
    mc "그러니까 건강한 음식이라고 하는 것들, 전부 녹색인 거 말이지."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:145
translate korean e08s01_ae0ca077:

    # arj "Well, it's mostly about preparation, isn't it? And what people are used to."
    arj "글쎄, 아마 대부분은 조리법 때문이겠지? 그리고 사람들이 익숙하지 않다는 점도 있겠고."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:146
translate korean e08s01_54dc2f02:

    # arj "Some people never tasted raw milk, but for me, it tastes better coming straight from the source, than the supermarket sourced stuff."
    arj "생유를 예로 들어 보자. 생유, 그러니까 미살균 우유를 평생 먹어 보지 못한 사람도 많고, 위험성 때문에 싫어하는 사람도 많지. 그치만, 나는 생유가 좋아. 슈머파켓에서 팔기 위해 각종 공정을 거친 우유보다 산지에서 바로 짠 우유가 나한텐 훨씬 맛있거든."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:148
translate korean e08s01_e7fc7dea:

    # mc "Yeah. I guess I never did grow out of my habits. I'm still used to that MegaBucks coffee."
    mc "그래. 나는 먹던 걸 쉽게 포기하진 못할 거 같은데. 난 아직도 메가벅스 커피가 그리운걸."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:151
translate korean e08s01_784b435e:

    # arj "Well, you're just proving my point. Nora's coffee wasn't just off the shelf stuff. It's artisanal."
    arj "흠, 내 요점이 바로 그거야. 노라 씨의 커피는 기성품이 아니었어. 바로 수제였지."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:152
translate korean e08s01_7d3b437c:

    # arj "Anything can taste weird if you don't prepare it. And it's always nice to try new things as well."
    arj "먹는 거든 마시는 거든 제대로 준비하지 않으면 이상한 맛이 되어 버리니까, 이상한 맛에 익숙해지기도 쉬운 거야. 그러니 항상 새로운 걸 시도해 보면서 제대로 된 맛을 경험해 보는 게 중요하다구."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:154
translate korean e08s01_f0ee82e7:

    # mc "I know. I never knew I would get used to this stuff."
    mc "그렇지. 나도 이런 일에 익숙해질 줄은 몰랐으니까."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:155
translate korean e08s01_ccc384ee:

    # arj "It was a new beginning for both of us."
    arj "우리 두 사람 모두 처음 해 보는 일이었는걸."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:158
translate korean e08s01_d6f346ee:

    # mc "The only issue I have with it is that left in the barn, it could lead to an explosion."
    mc "여하튼 이 일을 하면서 내가 걱정하는 건 헛간에 방치한 그 똥들이야. 그렇게 내버려 두면 폭발해 버릴 거라고."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:160
translate korean e08s01_14e98a30:

    # arj "Explosion?"
    arj "폭발?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:161
translate korean e08s01_a8989209:

    # mc "Yeah, if left in the barn, the nitrogen builds up and then the chemicals mix and match and it explodes."
    mc "그래, 헛간을 그대로 두면, 그 안에 질소가 축적되고 화학물이 혼합되서 폭발한다구."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:164
translate korean e08s01_52910354:

    # arj "How would you know that?"
    arj "그럴 거란 걸 어떻게 아는 거야?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:166
translate korean e08s01_efc1c52a:

    # mc "Basic chemistry."
    mc "기초적인 화학이잖아."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:167
translate korean e08s01_442bfd1f:

    # mc "You know, the number one leading cause of deaths on a farm is caused by random barn explosions."
    mc "너도 들어 봤을 거야, 농장에서 가장 흔한 사망 원인이 폭발이라는 거."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:170
translate korean e08s01_52ae2508:

    # mc "That's why people don't compost."
    mc "그래서 사람들이 퇴비를 만들지 않는 거라구."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:172
translate korean e08s01_e5c1b983:

    # arj "I doubt it. How does a barn randomly explode?"
    arj "의심스러운걸. 퇴비를 두었다고 헛간이 다 폭발하는 건 아니잖아, 그렇다면 무작위라는 거야?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:173
translate korean e08s01_b2959411:

    # mc "I don't know, that's why it's random."
    mc "나야 원인은 모르지, 그러니까 무작위라구."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:176
translate korean e08s01_bbb798c9:

    # arj "Sure. Random."
    arj "그러시겠지. 그래서 무작위라."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:178
translate korean e08s01_0bd0a6ab:

    # mc "I'm serious. There's a reason why people use feces for fuel."
    mc "난 진지하다구. 사람들이 분변을 연료 쓰는 덴 이유가 있겠지."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:179
translate korean e08s01_2b11944b:

    # arj "What, so we need to be careful around poop?"
    arj "어쨌든, 네 말의 요지는 우리가 똥을 신경 써야 한다는 소리니?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:182
translate korean e08s01_a1f81024:

    # mc "How we store it, yes."
    mc "그래, 퇴비로 쓸 거면 저장하는 방식에 신경을 쓰자는 거야."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:183
translate korean e08s01_a71061bf:

    # mc "Hey, I'm not as big of a dummy as you think I am."
    mc "어이, 네가 생각하는 것처럼 내가 완전히 등신은 아니거든."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:184
translate korean e08s01_3153d55a:

    # mc "I mean, sure, I'm not a hotshot engineer like you, but a business degree has its uses."
    mc "그러니까 내가 너처럼 대단한 공학자는 아니지만, 그래도 경영학 학위도 나름 쓸모는 있다구."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:187
translate korean e08s01_f9eb84a5:

    # arj "Engineering is an applied science, whereas business is not."
    arj "공학은 응용 과학이지만, 경영학은 아니잖니."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:188
translate korean e08s01_e9b2ee89:

    # arj "I don't think we need to advertise much for this job, anyway. The people come to us, not us to them."
    arj "마케팅 같은 건 농장일엔 필요 없다고 생각해. 농산품은 도매로 넘기는 거지, 소매로 파는 게 아니잖아."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:191
translate korean e08s01_de37dae0:

    # mc "You're living in the past. Stuck in the mud. Embrace the electronic age, baby."
    mc "그건 화석 수준의 고릿적 이야기라구. 우리는 정보화 시대에 살고 있다고, 자기야."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:192
translate korean e08s01_d85b8b35:

    # mc "We should host some sort of farmer's market and get the word out, so people buy from us directly."
    mc "우리는 농산물 직판장 같은 걸 열고 홍보를 해야 해. 소비자들이 우리 물건을 직접 사도록 말이야."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:195
translate korean e08s01_ffdf6ee4:

    # mc "Speaking of which, farmers."
    mc "말하자면, 농부들도 우리 물건을 사도록 말이야."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:197
translate korean e08s01_acf23214:

    # arj "*Whispers* Plus I don't think you're a dummy. I picked you after all, didn't I?"
    arj "*속삭이며* 그래 넌 바보가 아냐. 널 고른 건 결국 나인걸?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:198
translate korean e08s01_f39a644a:

    # mc "You made the right decision."
    mc "넌 옳은 선택을 했어."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:206
translate korean e08s01_eb313e0a:

    # ac "Morning."
    ac "좋은 아침이야."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:209
translate korean e08s01_298da376:

    # mc "Hello, Mr. and Mrs. Cooper."
    mc "안녕하세요, 쿠퍼 선생님과 여사님."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:212
translate korean e08s01_b815bf08:

    # ac "Mrs. Cooper? That makes me sound so old. I would use your last name if I knew what it was."
    ac "쿠퍼 여사님? 그렇게 말하니 내가 너무 나이 든 거 같다. 참, 너는 성이 뭐니?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:214
translate korean e08s01_d34e1b7d:

    # mc "Young."
    mc "영입니다."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:215
translate korean e08s01_26b7b119:

    # ac "That you are."
    ac "어울리는 성이네."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:218
translate korean e08s01_99b2c393:

    # fc "How are things on the ginger farm?"
    fc "요즘 붉은 머리 농장은 어떻나?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:220
translate korean e08s01_5c12820d:

    # arj "Oh, the usual."
    arj "아, 평소와 같죠."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:223
translate korean e08s01_01dbbbb9:

    # ac "I like your hat."
    ac "그 꽃 모자에 어울린다."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:225
translate korean e08s01_f915dcd4:

    # arj "[mcname] named it after me."
    arj "[mcname], 얘가 이 꽃을 주면서 제 이름을 붙여 준 거 있죠."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:228
translate korean e08s01_69a9d609:

    # ac "That's romantic. Frank never does any of that for me."
    ac "낭만적이기도 해라. 프랭크는 나한텐 그런 건 해 준 적이 없는데."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:230
translate korean e08s01_323a85e4:

    # fc "You never asked."
    fc "그런 부탁은 한 적 없잖아."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:231
translate korean e08s01_f110cb6a:

    # fc "Really. She never asked."
    fc "하는 말이 아니라, 이 사람이 그런 부탁을 한 적은 한 번도 없다니까."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:233
translate korean e08s01_fd56f638:

    # ac "See what I live with?"
    ac "내가 어떤 사람이랑 살고 있는지 알겠지?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:236
translate korean e08s01_7f97070f:

    # arj "Did you folks need anything? Can I get you something to drink?"
    arj "두 분 필요하신 거라도 있나요? 마실 거라도 좀 드릴까요?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:238
translate korean e08s01_c12458fc:

    # fc "We won't be staying too long. I came over to ask if you had any more of that wire fencing."
    fc "두 사람 시간을 많이 뺏지는 않겠네. 철조망 남는 게 있는지 물어보려고 왔거든."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:239
translate korean e08s01_4718aa32:

    # fc "The usual guy I get it from is at some auction, and I want to finish setting this up before the Vinovella versus Minerva Bay game."
    fc "바이노벨라 대 미너바 베이 경기 전에 울타리 치는 걸 마치려고 했는데, 자주 가는 농자재상이 경매 같은 델 갔다지 뭐야."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:241
translate korean e08s01_d21ed967:

    # mc "Is that tomorrow?"
    mc "경기가 내일인가요?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:243
translate korean e08s01_6650e8dd:

    # fc "Yeah. Don't you read the newspaper?"
    fc "맞네. 신문은 안 보나 보군?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:244
translate korean e08s01_8b61fb97:

    # mc "Not much."
    mc "거의 안 보죠."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:245
translate korean e08s01_3d761780:

    # fc "I'm making cheese curds."
    fc "참, 말을 안 했지. 우린 생치즈를 만들어."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:247
translate korean e08s01_cfa5f012:

    # ac "Homemade cheese curds."
    ac "손으로 만드는 생치즈."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:250
translate korean e08s01_72e95968:

    # mc "Do we have any more wire?"
    mc "우리 철조망 남은 거 있어?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:253
translate korean e08s01_11d2150a:

    # arj "I think so."
    arj "있을걸."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:256
translate korean e08s01_6f9f0827:

    # arj "Come with me, Frank."
    arj "프랭크 씨, 이쪽으로 오세요."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:263
translate korean e08s01_606bfc6f:

    # ac "So, what's a handsome, strapping fellow like you working on a farm like this?"
    ac "그래서, 너 같이 잘 생기고 건장한 친구가 어쩌다 이런 농장에서 일하게 된 거니?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:266
translate korean e08s01_baf6ab91:

    # mc "You know me. Homegrown and ready for work."
    mc "큰 이유가 있는 건 아니구요. 어쩌다 보니, 작물도 키우도 열심히 일도 하게 된 거죠."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:269
translate korean e08s01_993780f9:

    # ac "A young man like you ought to come over and do some work for me."
    ac "청년, 우리 집에도 들러서 날 위해서 일 좀 해 줘."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:270
translate korean e08s01_88bb02ca:

    # ac "Maybe we can spend some time together."
    ac "같이 시간 보내면 좋잖아."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:276
translate korean e08s01_ac6cb51e:

    # mc "If I wasn't naive, Mrs. Cooper, I would think you're hitting on me."
    mc "쿠퍼 부인, 누가 보면 저한테 꼬리친다고 생각하겠어요. 순진한 저야 그런 의도가 아니시라는 걸 알지만요."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:279
translate korean e08s01_54b4df69:

    # ac "Is that what I was doing?"
    ac "내가 그런 일을 하고 있었나?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:280
translate korean e08s01_70416007:

    # ac "I was just talking."
    ac "난 말만 했을 뿐인데."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:283
translate korean e08s01_c7a4a560:

    # mc "So was I."
    mc "저도 말을 듣고만 있었죠."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:286
translate korean e08s01_9be82f9e:

    # ac "Give this to AmRose for me."
    ac "이거 앰로즈한테 줘."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:289
translate korean e08s01_def0ad19:

    # mc "What is it?"
    mc "이건 뭔가요?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:291
translate korean e08s01_5582c124:

    # ac "What does it look like?"
    ac "뭐처럼 보여?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:294
translate korean e08s01_10b853df:

    # mc "No, I mean, which seeds are they?"
    mc "아니, 그러니까, 씨앗인 건 알겠는데요. 무슨 씨앗이에요?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:296
translate korean e08s01_fb6316ef:

    # ac "It's a surprise! You'll have to wait until they grow out to see what they are."
    ac "비밀! 키워서 뭔지 직접 확인해 봐. 기다리는 것도 재미있어."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:299
translate korean e08s01_83ff8f6d:

    # ac "For all you know, they're magic seeds that can grow money trees."
    ac "돈이 자라는 마법의 나무 씨앗일 수도 있잖니."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:300
translate korean e08s01_66df8773:

    # ac "Or they're just the regular money trees from China."
    ac "아니면 평범하게 잎 모양이 동전 모양인 나무일 수도 있고."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:302
translate korean e08s01_f899a236:

    # mc "Sounds like a real gamble, but I think I might know which one it is."
    mc "돈이라고 하니 진짜 도박 같네요. 둘 중 하나라면 무슨 씨앗인지는 알겠지만요"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:306
translate korean e08s01_c53e9436:

    # fc "I'll be heading off. Let's go."
    fc "그럼 가 볼게. 가자고."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:309
translate korean e08s01_31929400:

    # fc "Good seeing you guys. Say hi to the little lady for me. Where is she, anyway?"
    fc "만나서 반가웠네. 그 귀여운 녀석한테도 내가 왔다고 해 주고. 참, 그 녀석은 어디있나?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:311
translate korean e08s01_e9c220e4:

    # mc "Sleeping in the house."
    mc "집에서 자고 있죠."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:312
translate korean e08s01_a45f9705:

    # fc "I'll be sure to bring a treat for her next time I come over."
    fc "다음에 올 때는 그 녀석 줄 간식을 꼭 가져 오지."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:317
translate korean e08s01_c121c6f2:

    # ac "Well, you know where to find me."
    ac "흠, 날 찾아와도 되고."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:318
translate korean e08s01_c85a0fd1:

    # ac "Bye, AmRose."
    ac "또 봐, 앰로즈."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:320
translate korean e08s01_2a58ca71:

    # arj "See you later."
    arj "또 뵈요."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:323
translate korean e08s01_3629e496:

    # arj "So what'd you guys talk about?"
    arj "그래서 두 사람 무슨 이야기했어?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:325
translate korean e08s01_ae91a0d3:

    # mc "Oh, she was teasing me as usual."
    mc "아, 평소처럼 날 놀리시던데."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:326
translate korean e08s01_13bd736d:

    # arj "Teasing you?"
    arj "널 놀렸다고?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:329
translate korean e08s01_6f2e6726:

    # mc "You know. Mindless flirting, or least that's what I think it was."
    mc "알잖아. 별 생각 없이 추파를 던지는 거, 뭐 내가 느끼기엔 그랬다는 거지."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:331
translate korean e08s01_b719d9c4:

    # arj "Do you find her attractive?"
    arj "너 끌렸지?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:333
translate korean e08s01_7a6d41cc:

    # mc "Well, yeah."
    mc "음, 그랬지."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:336
translate korean e08s01_406f7aa0:

    # arj "So do I."
    arj "나도 끌리긴 했어."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:338
translate korean e08s01_dab106ef:

    # mc "You say that with everyone."
    mc "넌 누구한테나 끌리잖아."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:339
translate korean e08s01_34bdcdb2:

    # arj "Not everyone."
    arj "누구한테나 그러는 거 아니거든."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:342
translate korean e08s01_366e6865:

    # arj "It's not my fault people around here are so attractive."
    arj "이곳 사람들이 엄청 매력적인 게 내 잘못은 아니잖아."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:343
translate korean e08s01_a2a01c74:

    # arj "The old stereotype about rednecks isn't true. If only Hollywood came down here and saw people, they would move their production offices here."
    arj "옛날부터 시골 사람들이 이러니 저러니 하는 말은 아니더라니까. 헐리우드 사람들이 여기에 와서 이 사람들을 봤으면, 자기들 제작 부서를 이곳으로 옮겼을걸."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:346
translate korean e08s01_fdb36678:

    # mc "So I'm guessing Frank hit on you as well?"
    mc "그래서 프랭크 씨도 널 꼬시려고 했다는 거지?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:348
translate korean e08s01_fb5f01a8:

    # arj "No. We talked about which books we read."
    arj "아니. 우리는 서로 읽은 책 이야기했는데."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:349
translate korean e08s01_9c9b73e2:

    # mc "What were you reading?"
    mc "요즘 무슨 책 읽고 있었어?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:352
translate korean e08s01_d66e0b21:

    # arj "I recommended we both read Their Eyes Were Watching God."
    arj "그들의 눈은 신을 보고 있었다라는 책. 이 책을 읽어 보라고 추천했지."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:354
translate korean e08s01_a6e7ae0c:

    # mc "What's that? Some religious book?"
    mc "무슨 책인데? 무슨 종교서 같은 거야?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:356
translate korean e08s01_c4052139:

    # arj "No. It's about the life of a young black woman in the American South during the Civil War. Mostly about her life on the farm."
    arj "아니. 남북전쟁 당시 미국 남부의 젊은 흑인 여성의 삶에 관한 이야기를 다룬 책이야. 주로 이 여성이 농장에서 겪은 내용을 담고 있지."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:357
translate korean e08s01_1723eef2:

    # arj "You'd like it."
    arj "너도 마음에 들걸."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:360
translate korean e08s01_5e4c0ee2:

    # mc "Any exciting scenes?"
    mc "흥미로운 장면이라도 있어?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:362
translate korean e08s01_26e7ce04:

    # arj "There's a lot of sex building, and lots of sexual tension throughout."
    arj "성적 긴장감이 고조되는 부분이 정말 많거든. 책 전체에 성적 긴장감이 넘치고 넘친답니다."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:363
translate korean e08s01_501cda46:

    # arj "And a scene where there's a hurricane, though I'm not sure how realistic it is. The cows end up flying around."
    arj "허리케인이 나오는 장면이 있어. 얼마나 현실적인지 모르겠더라니까. 소들은 결국 하늘로 날라가 버리지."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:365
translate korean e08s01_6f0b96e7:

    # mc "I'll read it after you're done."
    mc "네가 다 읽으면 나도 읽어 볼게."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:368
translate korean e08s01_82907980:

    # arj "When we were in college, I'd practically force you to read these books, and now you're doing it out of free will."
    arj "대학 다닐 땐 억지로 책을 읽게 만들었어야 했는데. 이젠 스스로 읽게 됐구나."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:370
translate korean e08s01_077a8a76:

    # mc "I was never opposed to reading books, I just didn't have time to do it."
    mc "책 읽는 게 싫어서 그랬던 게 아니라, 책 읽는 시간이 없어서 그랬을 뿐이었거든."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:371
translate korean e08s01_d93dadf6:

    # mc "Now all we have is time."
    mc "이제 우리한테 있는 거라곤 시간뿐이잖아."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:375
translate korean e08s01_ef858acc:

    # arj "You're right."
    arj "그렇긴 하지."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:376
translate korean e08s01_98640f36:

    # arj "You ever stop and wonder about the things we have now?"
    arj "혹시 우리의 삶에 대해서 생각해 본 적 있어?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:379
translate korean e08s01_6ff67542:

    # mc "All the time. Farm life is slow and dull, and it leaves for a lot of thinking to do."
    mc "항상 하지. 농장에서 보내는 삶은 느리고 지루해서, 생각할 시간이 많으니까."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:381
translate korean e08s01_70dff08e:

    # arj "Did you mean it before, what you said? That you made the right decision?"
    arj "아까 한 말 진심이었어? 내가 옳은 선택을 했다는 거?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:382
translate korean e08s01_e89d42cd:

    # mc "I do. I have no regrets being with you. I'm so glad I'm here with you now, here and forever."
    mc "진심이지. 너와 함께한 걸 후회하지 않아. 지금 이곳에서 영원히 너와 함께 있을 수 있다는 게 정말 기쁜걸."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:385
translate korean e08s01_83078e78:

    # mc "I love you."
    mc "사랑해."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:387
translate korean e08s01_0c0a0443:

    # arj "I love you too."
    arj "나도 사랑해."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:390
translate korean e08s01_e430ce63:

    # arj "Let's finish up our work here and eat something."
    arj "이제 일 마무리하고 뭐 좀 먹자."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:391
translate korean e08s01_4987d2f4:

    # arj "I'm pooped."
    arj "지쳐서 이러나 피똥 싸겠다니까."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:393
translate korean e08s01_6a31178d:

    # mc "Hungry?"
    mc "배고파?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:394
translate korean e08s01_1e1cca5b:

    # arj "A bit. We should feed our girl too."
    arj "조금. 멍멍이한테도 밥 줘야지."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:401
translate korean e08s01_4efa488c:

    # arj "Remy's still sleeping."
    arj "레미는 아직도 자고 있네."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:407
translate korean e08s01_c82ccabf:

    # mc "You want what we made yesterday? Still have some leftovers."
    mc "어제 만든 거 먹을래? 남은 거 좀 있는데."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:409
translate korean e08s01_24c9bb5d:

    # arj "Alright."
    arj "좋아."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:413
translate korean e08s01_ffd29e47:

    # mc "That reminds me, I need to go back out into the barn after lunch."
    mc "까먹고 있었네. 점심 먹고 헛간에 가야겠다."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:415
translate korean e08s01_bd1ce1df:

    # arj "What for?"
    arj "왜?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:418
translate korean e08s01_fd71de68:

    # mc "Need to clean out the troughs. Forgot to do that."
    mc "물통 청소해야 돼. 깜빡했어."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:420
translate korean e08s01_beebfcce:

    # arj "I thought you did that yesterday."
    arj "물통 청소는 어제도 한 거 같은데."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:421
translate korean e08s01_c045360b:

    # mc "I did too. All shit out of luck."
    mc "그랬지. 벌써 더러워졌다니까. 내 팔자야."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:449
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_a0559298:

    # arj "Do you need any help?"
    arj "도와줄까?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:452
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_2f3e464b:

    # mc "I am good."
    mc "괜찮아."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:453
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_12aa2d25:

    # mc "I have a project in my mind. I'm thinking of expanding the barn a little more."
    mc "하려고 벼루던 것도 있거든. 헛간을 약간 확장할 생각이야."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:456
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_b22942bb:

    # arj "Expanding the barn?"
    arj "헛간을 확장한다고?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:458
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_913c8ce6:

    # mc "Yeah, you know, for the wintertime, so that we can store things a bit better there instead of leaving things out on the ground, on the snow."
    mc "맞아, 이제 곧 겨울이잖아. 땅바닥이나 눈 위에 물건을 그대로 둘 수는 없으니. 보관할 자리를 만들어야지."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:459
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_8396bda8:

    # arj "Might be a bit difficult."
    arj "힘들겠는걸."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:462
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_bda3bdd3:

    # mc "Yeah, I know. I'm taking my time with it."
    mc "그렇긴 하지. 그래서 천천히 해 보려고."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:465
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_f89c7d4b:

    # arj "Winter's just on the horizon."
    arj "근데 겨울이 코앞이잖아."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:468
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_7eefe29e:

    # mc "I know. I noticed once the problems start, they never stop. They just keep piling on."
    mc "맞아. 일은 해도 해도 끝이 없다니까. 계속 쌓이기만 하고 말이야."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:474
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_d16efc3b:

    # mc "I should ask Frank or someone in the community about how to set it up. I know he worked on something like this."
    mc "프랭크 씨나 마을 사람들한테 방법을 좀 물어봐야겠어. 비슷한 일을 해 본 적이 있다고 하던데."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:481
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_3238b91b:

    # arj "Yeah, Frank's a smart guy. Did you know he used to be a musician?"
    arj "그렇게 해, 프랭크 씨는 똑똑한 거 같더라. 음악가였다는 거 알았어?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:483
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_7ad16e43:

    # mc "Really? I've never seen him with an instrument."
    mc "진짜? 악기 들고 있는 모습은 본 적도 없는데."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:484
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_fdfd7218:

    # arj "He's a violinist."
    arj "바이올린 연주자였다고 하던걸."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:487
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_698d7569:

    # mc "Wow."
    mc "와아."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:489
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_81fa7c16:

    # arj "And Ashley plays the cello."
    arj "그리고 애슐리 씨는 첼로를 연주했대."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:490
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_93517230:

    # mc "Really? How do you know this and I don't?"
    mc "진짜? 어떻게 나만 모를 수가 있지?"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:493
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_332f1b09:

    # arj "They told me recently too. They were thinking about putting together a little folk ensemble and playing in public."
    arj "나한테도 최근에 알려 줬어. 아는 사람들이랑 작은 앙상블이라도 만들어서 공개 공연을 해 볼까 고민 중이라고 하더라."

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:495
translate korean e08s01_arj_back_abb6bf18:

